name: Astrogirl
description: Astrogirl is an Eastern Yilerus singer, recording artist, and dancer. After winning the fourth season of Terraria Got Talent, she was signed with ETH Entertainment in 4334 AYW. Her lead single, "Diamond Handz" charted in the top ten of the Yilerus Billboard Hot 100. Known for her wild dance moves, critics often compared Astrogirl with Supernova.
